evelopment of middle tier web services and SQL Server 2008-2016 objects, including complex stored procedures and functions.- Level 2 and Level 3 application support: from time to time, provide level 2 and level 3 application support for issues raised within the applications which your product group team owns. - This position will sometimes require after-hours and weekend availability.- Follow Agile methodologyEDUCATION:University or college degree/diploma in Computer Science, Engineering, Mathematics or equivalent work experience.  EXPERIENCE:- 7-10+ years web development experience- Angular2, Angular 1.X and JavaScript development experience- Knowledge of web application platforms, especially NodeJS or ASP.NET is required- Strong knowledge of web software development using one of more of ASP.NET, C#,WCF, HTML5, jQuery, ExtJS Sencha (assets)- Experience working with Microsoft SQL Server 2008 - 2016 objects, complex stored procedures, user defined functions, tables, queries, views, scripts, SQL backup processes, SQL agent, ETL, SSIS, BCP, SQL Profiler, SQL Server Management Studio, SQL Agent, SQL Profiler- Agile- Windows Communication Foundation (WCF)- Development of front end web and mobile applications- Development of database objects in SQL Server- Customer focussed- Ability to learn new technologies quickly and integrate them with existing applications and systems- Excellent English verbal and written communication skills - Excellent interpersonal skills FURTHER DETAILS:  

